description.standard: Summer’s on its way out, and you want it to end with a bang. Say no more: A$AP Ferg is here to help relaunch our It’s Lit! playlist, which has a brand-new look but is still packed with the hottest new turn-up tracks. A$AP Mob’s energy god is still raging in the glow of his new album Floor Seats—check “Wigs” and “Wam,” should you need convincing of his party-starting prowess—so he's handpicked a stack of tunes to keep the vibe going. "It’s like a Ferg concert,” he tells Apple Music. “Get off your ass! You have to move when these records play! If you’re driving, then the head-nodding has to to be extra special. If you’re at work or school, start dancing.” We keep It’s Lit! stocked with new music every week. Check back often, and if you hear something you like, add it to your library.
description.short: A$AP Ferg ends summer with a bang—and relaunches this party-focused playlist.
